AdIG7KOBZnwm-iAQo2Psr4cw&oe=673C6326"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_10_2560x1440.png", "id": "1183754672727348", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036618_1183754676060681_5949674915823822778_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zAu3i8rNNT0Q7kNvgHP_Ksh&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDa004GKdoaNTkwE0ZwuqB4DasMgTP8R8OWAbKu-5lgDA&oe=673C7281"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_02_2560x1440.png", "id": "1364811574301091", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035351_1364811577634424_4595682440016244285_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=9piL9rqMn_IQ7kNvgGrADkr&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDERfu3jOqPWT8z5OdqyPGLvf7qGBtiRRwWr-vvuHzCkA&oe=673C6F3F"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_06_2560x1440.png", "id": "1418447955596834", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570305_1418447958930167_1033562964254285107_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Asnwo9oNWgcQ7kNvgG5n_x0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBbBr08UNOtJAycrEYcSMSB3PYlA1AH2DRPryY4ea-IdA&oe=673C782F"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "TrailerCoverImage_2560x1440.png", "id": "528501706154977", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001660_528501709488310_7851645988733193620_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rUo8sauSwcUQ7kNvgFsF_im&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB_MB8wvEkF_KSc41WKI1o9eykF_asZ7mBLOpjjyFdYgw&oe=673C8940"}, "display_name": "Tennis Esports", "keywords": ["Training", "Physics", "Multiplayer", "Sports", "Tournaments"], "long_description": "The **free-to-download version of Tennis Esports** offers everything you need to connect, play, and enjoy tennis in a vibrant virtual world. Play endless matches, customize your avatar, and socialize with players from around the globe!\n\nMeet up with up to 10 friends in our **social clubs**, explore our **cooperative minigame area**, and enjoy **casual doubles**. You might even go head-to-head with a pro!\n\nWant to stand out on the court? Visit the in-game shop for exclusive outfits and gear to enhance your style.\n\nExplore and get a taste of the *Tennis Esports* universe with a selection of **AI matches, Courses, Arcade**, and the **TechZone** for **Forehand** and **Backhand** training. Take on limited multiplayer challenges.\n\n#### **Social Club**  \n- Casual courts for up to 4 players  \n- Cooperative minigame area\n- Limited match challenge invites \n- Accept unlimited match challenges from *Tennis Esports Premium* members  \n\n#### **Tennis Esports**  \n- Full avatar customization  \n- Limited courses\n- Limited AI challenges\n- MirrorPlay Classic \u2013 play against yourself  \n- HitEmAll Easy  \n- Forehand 101 Basics and Backhand 101 Basics  \n\nUnlock unlimited live matches, 10 AI opponents, 25+ training exercises, 6 arcade games, and more with **Tennis Esports Premium**!\n\nEnhance your skills with real tennis techniques\u2014explore our **TechZone Add-Ons** for advanced training, based on scientific research.\n\nDownload the app and join Discord \n\nhttps://discord.gg/8rcSArKJD4", "short_description": "Tennis Esports Free-to-Download. Play tennis in a vibrant virtual world with Tennis Esports! Enjoy matches, customize your avatar, and socialize globally. Meet friends in clubs, play casual matches, and explore the cooperative minigame area. Access limited AI matches, Courses, Arcade, and TechZone for basic forehand/backhand training. Upgrade to Premium for unlimited matches, 10 AI opponents, 25+ exercises, 6 arcade games, and more!\nJoin our Discord: https://discord.gg/8rcSArKJD4"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://tennis-esports.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://tennis-esports.com/legal", "publisher_name": "VR Motion Learning", "support_website_url": "https://www.tennis-esports.com/contacts", "website_